snippet.title: Fortnite OG: Chapter 1 - Season 1 - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Fortnite OG is back and here to stay. 

Drop into the original Chapter 1 - Season 1 map to experience classic Fortnite. 

Solos or Squads, drop into battle with Fortnite OG: Chapter 1. Build your way to pure victory in Battle Royale or dominate the Island in a new way with Zero Build. And stay tuned — Fortnite OG Ranked is coming soon!
